{"tid":1430370,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[香城online攻略] 滅火攻略update","createTime":"2019-08-07T17:19:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-29T17:29:27.000Z","uid":273265,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"32f1a9806d23c1f890ada4e5feddaa45da11ebe0","tid":1430370,"uid":273265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T17:19:57.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><ins>重點</ins></strong></span></span><br />\n一定要面向黑狗,同犬隻保持距離先好行動,有手足因滅火送頭<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/ChanKamShui/videos/359676988026474\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FChanKamShui%2Fvideos%2F359676988026474&d=zO4uXE7qxnklPfV4Vu9eJYPST22DtV%2BdF%2FIIxhOvvTQ%3D&h=a16a2209\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/ChanKamShui/videos/359676988026474</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: teal;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><ins>現有方法</ins></strong></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">1-用水淋</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=VAbrQZOcGDo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DVAbrQZOcGDo&d=zO4uXE7qxnklPfV4Vu9eJYPST22DtV%2BdF%2FIIxhOvvTQ%3D&h=a6f4db38\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=VAbrQZOcGDo</a><br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">2-反轉垃圾筒個底</span>,搵唔到片,但係就係將呢舊嘢反轉CUP住粒蛋<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1tGWzcT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1tGWzcT.jpg&h=59bdc4dc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">3-滅火筒</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=auC--I9yPHE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DauC--I9yPHE&d=zO4uXE7qxnklPfV4Vu9eJYPST22DtV%2BdF%2FIIxhOvvTQ%3D&h=eda3e1fd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=auC--I9yPHE</a><br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">4-餸碟</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kKTRn0k.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkKTRn0k.jpg&h=bf2e637e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">5-消防喉</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3wTU5kC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3wTU5kC.jpg&h=84e42c75&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: purple;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><ins>可行方法</ins></strong></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">1-水袋</span>,已有人測試降溫能力好高,但未實測<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AUd2uxh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAUd2uxh.jpg&h=9eea1788&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">2-大水樽</span>,重點在於放低幾個水樽,執粒蛋入去,機動性比攞住幾個大水樽周圍走高少少<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=D8C3Q-QwG4I\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DD8C3Q-QwG4I&d=zO4uXE7qxnklPfV4Vu9eJYPST22DtV%2BdF%2FIIxhOvvTQ%3D&h=ab57cb2a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=D8C3Q-QwG4I</a><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">3-可樂</span>,水壓加CO2,效果好好<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ENHCmypi7Ks\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DENHCmypi7Ks&d=zO4uXE7qxnklPfV4Vu9eJYPST22DtV%2BdF%2FIIxhOvvTQ%3D&h=870805fa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ENHCmypi7Ks</a><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">4-唧唧水樽</span>, 比普通水樽準,水壓都高D<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/d1Ztqer.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fd1Ztqer.jpg&h=639daffc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n請幫推 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22a02c2b0b25ad9b106970a0d085e7d1f930cef7","tid":1430370,"uid":273265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T17:21:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"202eb083397db488fafffc5669df108e4f2